title: Jena Dewan shares topless photos taken by Channing Tatum
text:
1 of 3 | License Photo LOS ANGELES, Oct. 9 (UPI) -- Jenna Dewan has shared a pair of stunning, topless photos taken by her husband, Channing Tatum .
The 34-year-old took to Instagram Thursday to reveal the sexy makeup-free shots while poking fun at her husband's photography skills.
The couple planned the outdoor photo shoot together while on vacation in Mexico.
"#tbt to chans insistence on a make-up-free shoot in Cabo...too bad he's not good at anything," the actress posted alongside a pic of herself staring into the camera with her arms folded over her breasts.

"I pretty much live my entire life with hair in my face," she wrote.
